import React from 'react'
import ToDoList from './ToDoList'

function Content() {
  return (
    <>
        <section className="main">
            <input className="toggle-all" type="checkbox" />
            <label htmlFor="toggle-all">
                Mark all as complete
            </label>
            <ToDoList/>
        </section>
    </>
  )
}

export default Content
